subTitle: Twins Sunil and Anil try to reunite their parents who separated many years ago due to a tragic misunderstanding regarding a friend's wish to have an abortion.

subTitle: When Lieutenant Suraj goes missing, his father believes he is dead and decides to keep the news from his daughter and his son's wife. However, they already know and choose to put up a brave front.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Deewaar
subTitle: Vijay leads a life of crime as a result of his troubled past, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest policeman.Things go awry when Ravi is sent to arrest Vijay.

subTitle: A cavalier young woman claims to be a businessman's fiancée and moves into his house. However, seizing the opportunity, the businessman plays along to make his true love jealous.

title: Mahaan

title: Shershaah

title: Hum Tumhare Hain Sanam
subTitle: Gopal is happily married to Radha until she meets her friend Suraj and starts obsessing over his singing career. Gopal suspects that they are secretly seeing each other and decides to leave her.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Judwaa
